        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/\">Loogle</a> is useful to search relevant lemmas.<br>\nAccording to <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=PosNum.ofNat\">the search result</a>, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=PosNum.ofNat#doc\">docs#PosNum.ofNat</a> has no lemmas.<br>\nAs in the <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Data/Num/Basic.html#PosNum\">docstring</a>, <code>PosNum</code> is basically unused and <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=PNat#doc\">docs#PNat</a> is more prefered, so it has poor API currently.</p>",
